K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-1: a'arya n'a ga ra aa ba la ma bi k'a n'a ma ma h'a y'a na s'u tra /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-3: 'phags pa grong khyer gyis 'tsho ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-7: bcom ldan 'das mnyam yod na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mngon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' rab na lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142a-24: dge ba snyen ma rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-0: mchod @142b cing rjed de padma chus ma gos pa bzhin du bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-1: de nas de'i tshe rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis de bzhin gshegs pa la mchod pa'i phyir ston zla tha chung zla ba nya ba'i tshes bco lnga la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-2: 'bru mar gyis zangs po che stong bkang ste dngar nas mar me spar ba'i 'od kyis khor khor yug tu dpag tshad bzhir snang bas khyab par byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-3: de nas yang de'i tshe mnyan yod kyi grong khyer chen po na dga' byed ma zhes bya ba grong khyer gyis 'tsho ba zhig 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-4: des 'bru mar sran gre'u dang sbyar ba nyos nas zhag bzhi kha 'tshos te nyam chung bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-5: de nas 'bru mar de khyer te rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal du song nas khyim gyi nang logs su mar me spar te bzhag nas 'di ltar sems bskyed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-7: bdag dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis ma 'ongs pa'i dus na ji ltar da ltar gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ji lta ba bzhin du bdag kyang ma 'ongs pa'i dus na ston par gyur te chos ston par gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-8: dge 'dun yang sdud par gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:142b-10: gal te bdag ma 'ongs pa'i dus na sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba zhig na mar me 'di bdag phyir ma 'ongs kyi bar du 'bar bar gyur cig ces byas nas mar me de spar te grong khyer du song na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-1: me de'i 'od zer kyis dzambu'i gling thams cad snang bar gyur te nam nangs kyi bar du'ang mar me de ma shi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-2: de nas tshe dang ldan pa moonggal gyi bu chen pos chos gos kyi mtha' mas mar me de gsad par byas nas gsad par ma nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-3: de nas tshe dang ldan pa moonggal gyi bu chen pos rnam par 'thor rlung gis gsad par byas kyang gsad par ma nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-4: de nas tshe dang ldan pa moonggal gyi bu chen pos tshangs pa'i 'jig rten du 'dug nas stong gsum 'dir shing rta'i srog shing tsam gyi char gyi rgyun dbab par byin gyis brlabs te mar me de yi steng du btang yang gsad par ma nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-5: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-8: mar me 'di ni byang chub kyi sems kyis sbar ba yin la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-9: byang chub kyi sems ni nyan thos kyis zil gyis mnan par mi nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-11: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi sems ni nyan thos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-12: rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis zil gyis mnan du med pa'i phyir ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-13: de nas re zhig na bud med de nyi ma shar te grong khyer nas phyir 'ongs nas des mar me de shin tu 'bar ba mthong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-14: des mchog tu dga' ba chen pos rgyas par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143a-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i tshe 'dzum pa mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-0: sangs rgyas bcom ldan @143b 'das rnams kyi chos nyid ni 'di yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-1: gang gi tshe sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'dzum pa mdzad pa de'i tshe sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi zhal gyi sgo nas 'od zer kha dog du ma /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-9: dngul gyi kha dog lta bu dag byung bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-10: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas mu med pa dag snang bas khyab par byas nas tshangs pa'i 'jig rten gyi bar du song ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-12: nyi ma'i 'od kyang zil gyis mnan nas yang slar log ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-13: bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tor du nub par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-14: de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das la tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos tshigs su bcad de gsol pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-16: rgyal mchog rnam par 'dren pa gang zag mchog /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-17: rgyu med par ni 'dzum pa mi mdzad na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-18: ci yi rkyen gyis zhal ni 'dzum mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-19: 'jig rten phan pa thugs brtses bdag la gsungs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:143b-22: grong khyer gyis 'tsho ba 'di bskal pa nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bar du ngan 'gro log par ltung bar 'gro bar mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-2: mi'i phun sum tshogs pa dag nyams su myong nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu snang ba zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i tshe tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-4: stobs bcu ldan pa mchod phyir zangs chen phrag stong gsal rgyal gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-5: mar me bzang po sbar bas dpag tshad bzhir ni kun tu snang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-6: grong khyer 'tsho ba'i 'bru mar sran ma gre'u sbyar spar ba yis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-7: 'dzam gling snang bas khyab gyur de ni byang chub sems kyi mthus //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-8: moonggal gyis ni mar me gsad 'dod rdzu 'phrul rgya chen byas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-9: rnam par 'thor ba'i rlung gi shugs btang gsad par yod ma nus //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-10: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten 'dug nas chu rgyun shing rta'i srog shing tsam //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-11: phab kyang gsad par ma nus mar me nyi ma'i 'od bzhin snang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-12: de ni zhag bzhi kha 'tshos rgyal byed dga' ba'i tshal du 'ongs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-13: dga' ba'i sems kyis bde gshegs zhabs la phyag byas thal sbyar 'dug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-14: mnyam med 'dzum pa mdzad pas kun dga' bo yang rab dga' nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-15: gzi brjid mtha' yas 'dzum mdzad 'di yi 'bras bu ji 'dra gsungs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-16: dga' byed 'di ni bskal pa nyi shu brgyad na rgyal bar 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144a-17: rang 'byung kun snang zhes bya 'od kyis stong chen bzhi snang byed //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-0: ma 'ongs dus na bde bar @144b gshegs pa bye ba mchod par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-1: de ni kun tu 'khor los bsgyur 'gyur rgyal rnams bkur stir byed //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-2: sangs rgyas rtogs pa brjod pa yi ni dad rnams rab dga' byed //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-3: skye bo mkhas pa dag gis de thos sems kyang rab tu dga'//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-4: de ltar rgyal ba bsam yas stobs bcu'i chos kyang bsam mi khyab //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-5: dga' ba bskyed na rnam smin mtshungs med bsam gyis mi khyab 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-7: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-8: grong khyer gyis 'tsho ba de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-9: byang chub sems dpa' de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-14: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-16: 'phags pa grong khyer gyis 'tsho ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-17: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzny'a na garbha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-18: lo ts'a ba bande klu'i dbang pos bsgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-19: rgya gar gyi mkhan po pi [?] dya ka ra sidha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-005:144b-20: zhus chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande de ba tsandra sa zhus te gtan la phab pa //
